These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, electrician
There are 2 different nationalities: german, polish
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, train
1. the electrician is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
2. the nurse is on the right of the electrician##1
3. the person driving the train is on the right of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea      | coffee    |
| Job           | electrician | nurse |
| Nationality   | german       | polish  |
| Transport     | tram      | train     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: pumpkin, grapes
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, reggae
2 different pets are kept: snake, mouse
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, subway
1. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
2. the person eating grapes is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | grapes | pumpkin |
| Music-Genre   | country       | reggae         |
| Pet           | mouse     | snake         |
| Transport     | subway    | roller    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: cooking, card-games
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, scientist
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, techno
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, trike
1. the fan of techno is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the nurse##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | card-games          | cooking |
| Job           | scientist | nurse     |
| Music-Genre   | d&b            | techno         |
| Transport     | trike         | roller   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
