The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, martial-arts
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, folk
2 different pets are kept: ferret, chinchilla
1. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
2. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the ferret##1
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | mirinda     | water   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts    | horror |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | folk |
| Pet           | ferret | chinchilla    |

