The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, rowing
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the indian##1
4. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror  | epic |
| Music-Genre   | pop     | soul      |
| Nationality   | nigerian | indian   |
| Sport         | rowing  | sailing |

