.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, cola
There 2 different types of food: watermelon, apricot
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, dubstep
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, ship
1. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person eating watermelon is the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is the person driving the ship##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | cola     | soy-milk |
| Food          | apricot   | watermelon |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep     | hip-hop     |
| Transport     | quad-bike | ship     |

 